  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下用户系统的整体架构流程图，核心是基于Gin框架的分层设计。最外层是Client API进来，先到Gin Router做路由分发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client API",
        "Gin Router"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，入口是Client API，然后连接到Gin Router。路由层下面应该分几个业务Handler对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client API",
        "Gin Router"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，三个核心Handler：Auth Handler处理登录鉴权，Profile Handler处理用户资料，Post Handler处理帖子内容。都从Gin Router分出去。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gin Router",
        "Auth Handler",
        "Profile Handler",
        "Post Handler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加三个Handler节点，都从Gin Router引出。接下来是Usecase层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auth Handler",
        "Profile Handler",
        "Post Handler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "每个Handler对应一个Usecase：Auth Usecase、Profile Usecase、Post Usecase。Handler只负责HTTP协议转换，业务逻辑下沉到Usecase。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auth Handler",
        "Profile Handler",
        "Post Handler",
        "Auth Usecase",
        "Profile Usecase",
        "Post Usecase"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三层结构有了。现在到Repository层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auth Usecase",
        "Profile Usecase",
        "Post Usecase"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Usecase下面挂Repository：User Repository给Auth用，Profile Repository给Profile用，Post Repository给Post用。注意Auth和User Repository是一对一，但Profile和Post各自独立。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auth Usecase",
        "Profile Usecase",
        "Post Usecase",
        "User Repository",
        "Profile Repository",
        "Post Repository"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：User Repository只连Auth Usecase，不直接给其他Usecase用？比如Profile修改时会不会也要操作用户表？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Repository",
        "Auth Usecase",
        "Profile Usecase"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前设计是解耦的，Profile Usecase只通过Profile Repository操作profile表，如果确实需要用户信息，走服务间调用而不是直接访问User Repository。保持边界清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Profile Usecase",
        "Profile Repository",
        "User Repository"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Repository层已画好。现在数据库层怎么设计？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Repository",
        "Profile Repository",
        "Post Repository"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "关键来了——我们做了读写分离。Master DB负责Write操作，Slave DB负责Read操作。三个Repository都要能连到这两个库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Repository",
        "Profile Repository",
        "Post Repository",
        "Master DB - Write",
        "Slave DB - Read"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是每个Repository同时连Master和Slave，还是说User Repository只写Master、只读Slave这种固定分工？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Repository",
        "Master DB - Write",
        "Slave DB - Read"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "每个Repository内部根据操作类型选择：写操作走Master DB，读操作走Slave DB。所以图上要画出User Repository、Profile Repository、Post Repository各自都有两条线分别指向Master和Slave。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Repository",
        "Profile Repository",
        "Post Repository",
        "Master DB - Write",
        "Slave DB - Read"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已画出三个Repository分别连接Master DB和Slave DB。那Master和Slave之间的Replication要体现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Master DB - Write",
        "Slave DB - Read"
